               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3681"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_richter_QGW_II_II_3681">Hanns Richter,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan">levit</roleName> dacz
                        sannd Stephan zu Wienn</rs>,</rs> dem <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien">Bürgermeister und Rath</rs>,</rs> dieweil er der
                  leviten stannd daselbs innhat, <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_peter-kapelle_st_valentin-messe_urbetsch">die
